_sText: Aim_CrossOver_Tsa v.102001 So yeah, this is pretty much going to turn into an awp war map but I still slapped in buyzones anyway. I'm not really sure if this map qualifies an "aim" map but I didn't know what to name it. Theres 40 spawn points and for fun I hid 5 bananas within the map as an easter egg. It's not that fancy of a map. Just something to get me back into mapping as it's been a while since my last release. I made a nav file although it's not that great haha. Anyway I hope you gentlemen enjoy it. I would have put in hdr to pretty up the map but apparently I can't play CS:S with DirectX9.0 graphics anymore :S I changed it to "mat_dxlevel 81" (so I could play online again with out my computer dying.) and when I changed it back to build cubemaps on hdr I was getting like, 1 frame per 20 seconds because my PC is amazing like that.
